<span class="text-on-surface-variant font-label text-[0.6875rem] uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">Premium Membership</span>
<div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-1">
<span class="text-4xl font-headline font-extrabold">$14.99</span>
<span class="text-on-surface-variant">/mo</span>
